You are helping build LUNÉVIA — a luxury AI-powered bridal beauty 
marketplace for Delhi. 

Stack: Next.js 14 App Router, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui, 
Framer Motion, Supabase, OpenAI API, Gemini API.

Design rules:
- Always use the LUNÉVIA color tokens from globals.css (--gold, --cream, --blush, --rose)
- Display text uses font-cormorant class, UI text uses font-dm-sans
- Animations use Framer Motion with duration 0.4s ease-in-out
- Cards always have: rounded-2xl, border border-gold/20, shadow-warm
- Never use generic blue/purple color schemes
- Always write TypeScript with proper types, no 'any'
- API routes go in /app/api/, never call AI APIs from client components

Component rules:
- shadcn components are the base — always reskin with LUNÉVIA tokens
- Skeleton loaders on every async data fetch
- Mobile-first: design at 375px, enhance for desktop